        text: "'"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'Public Function BitsShiftRight(ByVal Value As Long, ByVal ShiftCount As Long) As Long"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'  ' Shifts the bits to the right the specified number of positions and returns the new value."
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'  ' Bits \"falling off\" the right edge do not wrap around. Fill bits coming in from left match bit 31 (the sign bit): if bit 31 is 1 the fill bits will be 1 (see ShiftRightZ for the alternative zero-fill-in version)."
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'  ' A shift right is effectively a division by 2 (rounding downward, see Examples). Some common languages like C/C++ or Java have an operator for this job: \">>\""
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'  Select Case ShiftCount"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'    Case 0&:  BitsShiftRight = Value"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'    Case 1&:  BitsShiftRight = (Value And &HFFFFFFFE) \\ &H2&"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'    Case 2&:  BitsShiftRight = (Value And &HFFFFFFFC) \\ &H4&"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'    Case 3&:  BitsShiftRight = (Value And &HFFFFFFF8) \\ &H8&"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'    Case 4&:  BitsShiftRight = (Value And &HFFFFFFF0) \\ &H10&"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'    Case 5&:  BitsShiftRight = (Value And &HFFFFFFE0) \\ &H20&"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'    Case 6&:  BitsShiftRight = (Value And &HFFFFFFC0) \\ &H40&"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'    Case 7&:  BitsShiftRight = (Value And &HFFFFFF80) \\ &H80&"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'    Case 8&:  BitsShiftRight = (Value And &HFFFFFF00) \\ &H100&"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'    Case 9&:  BitsShiftRight = (Value And &HFFFFFE00) \\ &H200&"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'    Case 10&: BitsShiftRight = (Value And &HFFFFFC00) \\ &H400&"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'    Case 11&: BitsShiftRight = (Value And &HFFFFF800) \\ &H800&"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'    Case 12&: BitsShiftRight = (Value And &HFFFFF000) \\ &H1000&"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'    Case 13&: BitsShiftRight = (Value And &HFFFFE000) \\ &H2000&"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'    Case 14&: BitsShiftRight = (Value And &HFFFFC000) \\ &H4000&"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'    Case 15&: BitsShiftRight = (Value And &HFFFF8000) \\ &H8000&"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'    Case 16&: BitsShiftRight = (Value And &HFFFF0000) \\ &H10000"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'    Case 17&: BitsShiftRight = (Value And &HFFFE0000) \\ &H20000"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'    Case 18&: BitsShiftRight = (Value And &HFFFC0000) \\ &H40000"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'    Case 19&: BitsShiftRight = (Value And &HFFF80000) \\ &H80000"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'    Case 20&: BitsShiftRight = (Value And &HFFF00000) \\ &H100000"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'    Case 21&: BitsShiftRight = (Value And &HFFE00000) \\ &H200000"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'    Case 22&: BitsShiftRight = (Value And &HFFC00000) \\ &H400000"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'    Case 23&: BitsShiftRight = (Value And &HFF800000) \\ &H800000"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'    Case 24&: BitsShiftRight = (Value And &HFF000000) \\ &H1000000"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'    Case 25&: BitsShiftRight = (Value And &HFE000000) \\ &H2000000"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'    Case 26&: BitsShiftRight = (Value And &HFC000000) \\ &H4000000"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'    Case 27&: BitsShiftRight = (Value And &HF8000000) \\ &H8000000"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'    Case 28&: BitsShiftRight = (Value And &HF0000000) \\ &H10000000"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'    Case 29&: BitsShiftRight = (Value And &HE0000000) \\ &H20000000"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'    Case 30&: BitsShiftRight = (Value And &HC0000000) \\ &H40000000"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'    Case 31&: BitsShiftRight = CBool(Value And &H80000000)"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'  End Select"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'End Function"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'Public Function BitsShiftRightZ(ByVal Value As Long, ByVal ShiftCount As Long) As Long"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'  '- Shifts the bits to the right the specified number of positions and returns the new value."
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'  '- Bits \"falling off\" the right edge do not wrap around. Fill bits coming in from left are 0 (zero, hence \"ShiftRightZ\", see ShiftRight for the alternative signbit-fill-in version)"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'  If Value And &H80000000 Then"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'    Select Case ShiftCount"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'      Case 0&:  BitsShiftRightZ = Value"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'      Case 1&:  BitsShiftRightZ = &H40000000 Or (Value And &H7FFFFFFF) \\ &H2&"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'      Case 2&:  BitsShiftRightZ = &H20000000 Or (Value And &H7FFFFFFF) \\ &H4&"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'      Case 3&:  BitsShiftRightZ = &H10000000 Or (Value And &H7FFFFFFF) \\ &H8&"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'      Case 4&:  BitsShiftRightZ = &H8000000 Or (Value And &H7FFFFFFF) \\ &H10&"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'      Case 5&:  BitsShiftRightZ = &H4000000 Or (Value And &H7FFFFFFF) \\ &H20&"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'      Case 6&:  BitsShiftRightZ = &H2000000 Or (Value And &H7FFFFFFF) \\ &H40&"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'      Case 7&:  BitsShiftRightZ = &H1000000 Or (Value And &H7FFFFFFF) \\ &H80&"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'      Case 8&:  BitsShiftRightZ = &H800000 Or (Value And &H7FFFFFFF) \\ &H100&"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'      Case 9&:  BitsShiftRightZ = &H400000 Or (Value And &H7FFFFFFF) \\ &H200&"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'      Case 10&: BitsShiftRightZ = &H200000 Or (Value And &H7FFFFFFF) \\ &H400&"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'      Case 11&: BitsShiftRightZ = &H100000 Or (Value And &H7FFFFFFF) \\ &H800&"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'      Case 12&: BitsShiftRightZ = &H80000 Or (Value And &H7FFFFFFF) \\ &H1000&"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'      Case 13&: BitsShiftRightZ = &H40000 Or (Value And &H7FFFFFFF) \\ &H2000&"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'      Case 14&: BitsShiftRightZ = &H20000 Or (Value And &H7FFFFFFF) \\ &H4000&"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'      Case 15&: BitsShiftRightZ = &H10000 Or (Value And &H7FFFFFFF) \\ &H8000&"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'      Case 16&: BitsShiftRightZ = &H8000& Or (Value And &H7FFFFFFF) \\ &H10000"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'      Case 17&: BitsShiftRightZ = &H4000& Or (Value And &H7FFFFFFF) \\ &H20000"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'      Case 18&: BitsShiftRightZ = &H2000& Or (Value And &H7FFFFFFF) \\ &H40000"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'      Case 19&: BitsShiftRightZ = &H1000& Or (Value And &H7FFFFFFF) \\ &H80000"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'      Case 20&: BitsShiftRightZ = &H800& Or (Value And &H7FFFFFFF) \\ &H100000"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'      Case 21&: BitsShiftRightZ = &H400& Or (Value And &H7FFFFFFF) \\ &H200000"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'      Case 22&: BitsShiftRightZ = &H200& Or (Value And &H7FFFFFFF) \\ &H400000"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'      Case 23&: BitsShiftRightZ = &H100& Or (Value And &H7FFFFFFF) \\ &H800000"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'      Case 24&: BitsShiftRightZ = &H80& Or (Value And &H7FFFFFFF) \\ &H1000000"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'      Case 25&: BitsShiftRightZ = &H40& Or (Value And &H7FFFFFFF) \\ &H2000000"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'      Case 26&: BitsShiftRightZ = &H20& Or (Value And &H7FFFFFFF) \\ &H4000000"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'      Case 27&: BitsShiftRightZ = &H10& Or (Value And &H7FFFFFFF) \\ &H8000000"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'      Case 28&: BitsShiftRightZ = &H8& Or (Value And &H7FFFFFFF) \\ &H10000000"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'      Case 29&: BitsShiftRightZ = &H4& Or (Value And &H7FFFFFFF) \\ &H20000000"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'      Case 30&: BitsShiftRightZ = &H2& Or (Value And &H7FFFFFFF) \\ &H40000000"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'      Case 31&: BitsShiftRightZ = &H1&"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'    End Select"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'  Else"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'    Select Case ShiftCount"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'      Case 0&:  BitsShiftRightZ = Value"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'      Case 1&:  BitsShiftRightZ = Value \\ &H2&"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'      Case 2&:  BitsShiftRightZ = Value \\ &H4&"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'      Case 3&:  BitsShiftRightZ = Value \\ &H8&"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'      Case 4&:  BitsShiftRightZ = Value \\ &H10&"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'      Case 5&:  BitsShiftRightZ = Value \\ &H20&"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'      Case 6&:  BitsShiftRightZ = Value \\ &H40&"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'      Case 7&:  BitsShiftRightZ = Value \\ &H80&"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'      Case 8&:  BitsShiftRightZ = Value \\ &H100&"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'      Case 9&:  BitsShiftRightZ = Value \\ &H200&"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'      Case 10&: BitsShiftRightZ = Value \\ &H400&"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'      Case 11&: BitsShiftRightZ = Value \\ &H800&"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'      Case 12&: BitsShiftRightZ = Value \\ &H1000&"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'      Case 13&: BitsShiftRightZ = Value \\ &H2000&"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'      Case 14&: BitsShiftRightZ = Value \\ &H4000&"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'      Case 15&: BitsShiftRightZ = Value \\ &H8000&"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'      Case 16&: BitsShiftRightZ = Value \\ &H10000"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'      Case 17&: BitsShiftRightZ = Value \\ &H20000"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'      Case 18&: BitsShiftRightZ = Value \\ &H40000"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'      Case 19&: BitsShiftRightZ = Value \\ &H80000"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'      Case 20&: BitsShiftRightZ = Value \\ &H100000"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'      Case 21&: BitsShiftRightZ = Value \\ &H200000"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'      Case 22&: BitsShiftRightZ = Value \\ &H400000"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'      Case 23&: BitsShiftRightZ = Value \\ &H800000"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'      Case 24&: BitsShiftRightZ = Value \\ &H1000000"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'      Case 25&: BitsShiftRightZ = Value \\ &H2000000"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'      Case 26&: BitsShiftRightZ = Value \\ &H4000000"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'      Case 27&: BitsShiftRightZ = Value \\ &H8000000"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'      Case 28&: BitsShiftRightZ = Value \\ &H10000000"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'      Case 29&: BitsShiftRightZ = Value \\ &H20000000"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'      Case 30&: BitsShiftRightZ = Value \\ &H40000000"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'      Case 31&: BitsShiftRightZ = &H0&"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'    End Select"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'  End If"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'End Function"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'Public Function PopCount(ByVal x As Long) As Long"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'  ' for positive values only"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'  Debug.Assert x >= 0"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'  PopCount = 0"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'  Do While x > 0"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'    PopCount = PopCount + 1: x = x And (x - 1)"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'  Loop"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'End Function"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'Public Function And64(Op1 As TBit64, Op2 As TBit64) As TBit64"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'  And64.i0 = Op1.i0 And Op2.i0"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'  And64.i1 = Op1.i1 And Op2.i1"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'  And64.i2 = Op1.i2 And Op2.i2"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'  And64.i3 = Op1.i3 And Op2.i3"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'End Function"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'Public Function Or64(Op1 As TBit64, Op2 As TBit64) As TBit64"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'  Or64.i0 = Op1.i0 Or Op2.i0"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'  Or64.i1 = Op1.i1 Or Op2.i1"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'  Or64.i2 = Op1.i2 Or Op2.i2"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'  Or64.i3 = Op1.i3 Or Op2.i3"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'End Function"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'Public Function Xor64(Op1 As TBit64, Op2 As TBit64) As TBit64"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'  Xor64.i0 = Op1.i0 Xor Op2.i0"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'  Xor64.i1 = Op1.i1 Xor Op2.i1"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'  Xor64.i2 = Op1.i2 Xor Op2.i2"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'  Xor64.i3 = Op1.i3 Xor Op2.i3"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'End Function"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'Public Sub Clear64(Op1 As TBit64)"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'  Op1.i0 = 0"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'  Op1.i1 = 0"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'  Op1.i2 = 0"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'  Op1.i3 = 0"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'End Sub"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'"
      - kind: Newline
